channel.title: Few Questions about a Blank Source
channel.description:
I recently downloaded a Blank source. (I like to customize)
Anyways...
I have had several requests for a bank, and some Shops.
When I try and search the [b]makeGlobalObject[/b] there isn't one, and Idk how to make a item?
Also, For the shops... In the server files, there isn't a [b]Wannashop = 2[/b] So how would I add it?
The reason I ask of help is because I don't want to mess the server up.
Thanks very much! :D
